hike at the current time with the finance ministry 
the newspaper asahi shimbun reported the bank was considering a 
hike in its key lending rate by 07510 percentage points to stem 
inflationary pressures caused by rising oil prices due to the 
persian gulf crisis 
prices remain stable at the present time but higher oil 
