ishkhanian was run over by a vehicle without plates and was in 
critical condition hovannisian said 
it was unclear if ishkhanian was hit deliberately but 
hovannisian said the parliament stood for a moment of silence for 
both aivazian and ishkhanian before unanimously adopting the state 
of emergency 
parliament also banned the armenian national army which was 
formed in january and claims to protect armenians from attacks by 
