it was the socalled holy men who didnt accept christ and turned 
him in blinderman said jesus said judge not and i 
recommend that these people follow the precepts of the god they are 
proclaiming 
the tongues of flame exhibit opened at blindermans gallery 
earlier this year and is now appearing at the santa monica museum 
of art in california 
