institute told a news conference here that the nea had 
unconstitutionally used taxpayers funds to engage in actions 
which are hostile toward religion and religious persons 
the government should not become the patron of hate art 
against some of its citizens whitehead said religious people 
must no longer be the personal targets of cannon fire from national 
endowment projects 
