both planes have smooth contours to reduce their radar 
reflections and are built of advanced composite materials 
the pentagon wants a fighter plane that can fly twice the speed 
of sound without using fuelguzzling afterburners but it must also 
be highly maneuverable for dogfights with other planes and use 
radarevading stealth technology 
the lockheed plane resembles the navys fa18 hornet 
fighterattack aircraft with stubby wings 
the northrop plane is longer with a cigarlike fuselage and a 
wingspan that from overhead looks like a kite 
