to ensure supply levels before market introduction 
in introducing the new macintoshs apple wont completely 
discontinue its existing cheap macintosh computers the macintosh 
plus and the macintosh se a move that could leave computer owners 
with obsolete machines 
one of the things we havent done since 1984 when we first 
introduced macintoshes was to obsolete anything cook said 
