will compound the decline in months ahead 
we will be facing a few months of significant weakness because 
of the runup in rates said robert villanueva forecasting 
director for the national association of home builders 
at least for the remainder of the year its difficult to be 
optimistic said james nelson presidentelect of the mortgage 
