after testing its machinery and engines he will be aboard during 
the sea trials 
after the trials are finished chassin said the ship and its 
20member crew will return to san diego for supplies before sailing 
to singapore 
in singapore it will take on additional fuel and provisions 
and then go to egypt and the middle east load crude and then 
unload in france the united kingdom and rotterdam chassin said 
it will not load iraqi crude in turkey 
